      • didMethodFail

        public boolean didMethodFail(Machine machine,
                             java.lang.String methodName)
        Does a Machine.Method fail and returns if it failed or not (true if VMError is thrown) Uses reflection so that this one method could be called in place of having the code repeated over and over again for each method.
        Parameters:
        machine - Machine object
        methodName - name of method to check
        Returns:
        true if method failed
